# Make me sway #

31
00:07:29,265 --> 00:07:33,395
# Like a lazy ocean
hugs the shore #

32
00:07:33,436 --> 00:07:35,631
# Hold me close #

33
00:07:35,672 --> 00:07:38,436
# Sway me more #

34
00:07:38,474 --> 00:07:42,740
# Like a flower
bending in the breeze #

35
00:07:42,779 --> 00:07:45,179
# Bend with me #

